@startuml
title Recognition Event Submission Workflow

participant Camera
participant "Recognition agent" as Agent
participant "LBPH recognizer" as Recognizer
participant "Local SQLite queue" as Queue
participant "Backend API" as Backend
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Admin frontend" as Frontend

Camera -> Agent : frame
Agent -> Recognizer : recognize_face(frame)
Recognizer --> Agent : recognized?, person_id,\nLBPH distance, threshold
alt recognized and access enabled locally
  Agent -> Agent : open door
  Agent -> Queue : save recognized event
else unknown or denied
  Agent -> Queue : save unknown/denied event
end
Agent -> Backend : POST /api/v1/events or sync batch
Backend -> DB : persist AccessEvent
Backend --> Agent : accepted response
Frontend -> Backend : GET /api/v1/events
Backend -> DB : query recent events
Backend --> Frontend : events with raw distance

@enduml
